race.comment: Very moderate middle distance where COLLATED (1) won't get a better chance to break through. Fitter for two runs back, finishing fifth at both, and will find this much easier. Extra trip a plus, has the claim and with blinkers added should go close. SEA TREASURES (7) was midfield in richer company last time and went better than it looks off a wide draw. Much better gate here and well weighted with the claim. Looks a big improver. CULLEN SKINK (2) is fitter for three runs in, the latest fifth behind Guru Warrior in richer company. Ready now and looks placed to feature in the finish. FLYING ASSASSIN (3) tends to mix form but has the ability. Goes very well around this circuit and can do much better. LIFT THE BAR (4) got back and ran on late last time and is in the mix on best.
